<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10106127>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–6. Belladessus species morphology. 1–3) B. femineus: 1) Habitus; 2) Left metacoxa, metatrochanter, and metafemur; 3) Female reproductive tract, ventral aspect. 4–6) B. puella: 4) Habitus; 5) Left metacoxa, metatrochanter, and metafemur; 6) Female reproductive tract, ventral aspect. Scale bar = 1 mm for Figs. 1 and 4." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10106127/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

